replies.body:
I also reinstalled yesterday and it started working again.  Then this evening when I went to play, the error came back.  I realized that it only happens when I play ezreal.  In the logs, I'm getting the same errors but I'm also getting;

 "ERROR| Riot::RADS::IO::OpenFile: RADS cannot open file "Global/Champions/champions.bin" because it's not in the manifest." 

Which I believe is where the actual problem is.  Let me know if it's happening to you for only one champ and if you're getting the same error in the logs.
